    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and documented. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the intended simulation use at model risk level 3 under the ASME V&V 40-2018 framework. The assessment team accepts the package with the noted limitation on test condition coverage.",
